data.description: Location! Location! Location! Solid Brick Home Situated in Duquesne Heights steps to the overlook & Incline! Mature landscaping adds great curb appeal. Step onto the covered patio w/ porch swing. Large entry w/1st flr 1/2 bath. Triple pane windows thruout. Spacious living room w/electric fireplace. Furnace & AC less than a year old. Roof 3 years old. Grand dining room to host meals. Adorable sunroom w/HW floors leads to the back deck w/brand new 24X12 heated pool perfect for summer entertaining! Plus Hot Tub! Kitchen boasts Oak Cabinetry & SS appliances. Oak Steps to LL family room & 1/2 bath. Walk out to backyard. Newer 200 AMP Electric Service & Sewer Line. Full bath updated w/oak cabinetry & new plumbing. Large owner's suite w/ceiling fan.  A few personal touches will go a long way in this home. All major mechanicals are done for you! Walk to restaurants, enjoy fireworks this summer, take the incline to the city, the possibilities are endless! Great for an Air BNB or family home!
